---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy for zenprocess.ai (KMV Group LLC). Effective September 14, 2025."
>
  <section class="py-20 bg-[#000510]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-[#978aa1] mb-12">Effective: September 14, 2025</p>

      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8 text-[#f5f4f0]/80 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          KMV Group LLC, doing business as zenprocess.ai ("we," "us," or "our"), respects your privacy.
          This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, and share personal information when you
          visit zenprocess.ai or use our services.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Information We Collect</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Contact information you provide (name, email, phone, company)</li>
          <li>Information submitted through booking forms or contact forms</li>
          <li>Usage data collected via Google Analytics (anonymized)</li>
          <li>Device and browser information</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>To respond to inquiries and schedule discovery calls</li>
          <li>To provide and improve our services</li>
          <li>To analyze website usage and optimize user experience</li>
          <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Data Sharing</h2>
        <p>We do not sell your personal information. We may share information with:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Service providers who assist in our operations (GoHighLevel, Google Analytics)</li>
          <li>Payment processors (Stripe) for billing purposes</li>
          <li>As required by law</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Your Rights (CCPA/CPRA)</h2>
        <p>California residents have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Know what personal information we collect</li>
          <li>Request deletion of personal information</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
          <li>Opt out of the sale of personal information (we do not sell data)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          For privacy inquiries, contact us at
          <a href="mailto:info@zenprocess.ai" class="text-[#22C55E] hover:text-[#16A34A]">info@zenprocess.ai</a>
          or call <a href="tel:+18329742818" class="text-[#22C55E] hover:text-[#16A34A]">(832) 974-2818</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
